<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When Zend_Db_Row::save() is called using Zend_Db_Adapter_Oracle, the row in database does not update. This works fine in 1.9.3PL1.</p>

<p>The row does not get updated even though the Zend_Db_Adapter_Abstract::update() statement returns a positive number of affected rows.</p>

